                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-10-19T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 19, 1914, 6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>301. Your 43, September 29, cancellation mining titles, encloses only translation
                    of Circular No. 1 of September 3, by Department of Fomento. Department desires
                    decree of August 29.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Robert Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
